children.subject: 182 was definitely one of the hottest classes this semester (if it is on your list, definitely go for phrase 1). For Sp20, it filled up three days into phrase 1. Moreover, Professor Canny removed everyone on the waitlist after the semester began, as the class cannot accommodate more people.

170, 188 (depends on semester, this semester I think they took everyone from the waitlist but Fall 2019 they did not), 161, maybe 186 (previous semesters seemed to not have a problem getting into, but this time there seems to be a waitlist building up), and maybe 182 (not too sure about this one but most people generally don't take it/think about taking it)?

Sadly it seems like the classes are filling up earlier and earlier every semester

history.content: Hey guys, so I'm currently doing a CS Minor, and I'll have finished up the lower div classes by the end of next semester. What are the easiest upper divs to get into, since I don't have priority registration and will have to Phase I waitlist. I know CS 170 generally expands, but what other options do I have?
